Help

Everything is extremely simple.

First of all, you should remember appearing colors and their order.

Then, you should recall and restore it.

For each correctly restored color you get from 1 to 10 points. Once you guessed one color correctly, you obtain 1 point. If, after that, you guessed a second one in a row, you obtain 2 points. For a third one — 3 ones, and so on up to 10 points.

Once you make a mistake, the next guessed color will be evaluated for 1 point.

That's all.
